Pod::Simple::RTF \-\- format Pod as RTF
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 3
\&  perl \-MPod::Simple::RTF \-e \e
\&   "exit Pod::Simple::RTF\->filter(shift)\->any_errata_seen" \e
